name: Hero's Rule 1: Five Freedoms
description: Target up to 5 cards in any GY(s); banish them. If this card is in your GY, except the turn it was sent there: You can banish it, then target 1 of your banished "Elemental HERO" monsters; Special Summon it, ignoring its Summoning conditions. You can only use this effect of "Hero's Rule 1: Five Freedoms" once per turn.
